com.viaoa.jsp

Class OAGrid

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.jsp.OAGrid
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, java.io.Serializable

    public class OAGrid
extends java.lang.Object
implements OAJspComponent
    Grid component that will scroll equal sized cells. A template can be defined that will be filled out for each cell. Tags can then be used to embed other components, like servletImages and htmlElemets, or property paths.
    Author:
    vvia
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
